            "__cdata": "<p class=\"p_20\">5. A newborn baby presented with profuse bleeding from umbilical stump after birth. activated partial thromboplastin time (aPTT) and prothrombin time (PT) are normal. What is the most likely Probable diagnosis?</p>"
