            "__cdata": "<p class=\"p_20\">37. A patient presents with increased bilirubin, LDH, and reticulocyte count and decreased platelet count of 30,000.<br />\nCreatinine level is elevated, and smear is positive for schistocytes. There is no history of diarrhea. <br />\nWhat is the next step in management?</p>"
